		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<h3><strong>Do you wish to be a part of the ASIS team? Go ahead and tell us about it!</strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Careers at ASIS?<br />
ASIS &#8211; Shirdi Industries Ltd., a pioneer in the MDF, Particle Boards, ply and decorative laminates business, is an ever- growing organization that gives everybody ample scope to grow. We believe our real capital is our employees, and we believe in our philosophy of inclusive growth. Come and get an opportunity to work with our highly talented and professionally supportive personnel!</p>

		</div> 
